  m_TableData:
  - m_Id: 5018822381568
    m_Localized: Kill the marked piece immediately.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5018847547392
    m_Localized: Force a piece in a 6 squares radius to step forth 3 squares or until
      meeting an obstacle. The controlled piece will switch side.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5018847547393
    m_Localized: Stuns all adjacent enemy pieces in 1 turn.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5018847547394
    m_Localized: Upgrade an allied piece into another piece in the immediate upper
      rank. A champion will change into another champion instead.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5018847547395
    m_Localized: Bound an enemy at a distance of 5 squares for 1 turn.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5018847547396
    m_Localized: Grant a Shield to an ally in a 2 squares radius.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5018847547397
    m_Localized: Resurrect a captured Swarm or Common-ranked ally.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5018847547398
    m_Localized: Explode and kill itself, dealing 1 stack of Poison to any adjacent
      enemies.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5018847547399
    m_Localized: Gain Snapping Strike on the next turn.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5018847547400
    m_Localized: Afflicts all adjacent enemy pieces with 1 stack of Poison.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5018847547401
    m_Localized: Dash 2 squares in any orthogonal or diagonal direction, unblockable
      by any other pieces. Any enemy lies on the path will be stunned for 1 turn
      and gain one stack of Poison.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5018847547402
    m_Localized: Resurrect a captured Sea Star. The resurrected piece will not be
      able to use skill.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5018847547403
    m_Localized: Taunt an enemy for 3 turns.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 60977664922931200
    m_Localized: Force an enemy in a 6-square radius to step up 3 squares, then apply
      Controlled to them.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
